    "content": "# Getting Started with Your Widget\r\n\r\n## Quick Start Guide\r\n\r\n### 1. Unboxing & Hardware Setup\r\n1. **Package Contents**\r\n   - Widget device\r\n   - USB-C power adapter\r\n   - Quick start guide\r\n   - Mounting brackets (Pro/Enterprise)\r\n   - Ethernet cable (Pro/Enterprise)\r\n\r\n2. **Physical Setup**\r\n   - Remove protective films\r\n   - Insert included battery\r\n   - Connect power adapter\r\n   - Press power button for 3 seconds\r\n\r\n### 2. Initial Configuration\r\n\r\n#### Mobile App Setup\r\n1. **Download the App**\r\n   - iOS: App Store (iOS 14.0+)\r\n   - Android: Google Play Store (Android 11.0+)\r\n\r\n2. **Create Account**\r\n   - Open widget app\r\n   - Select \"Create Account\"\r\n   - Enter email and password\r\n   - Verify email address\r\n\r\n3. **Connect Your Widget**\r\n   - Enable Bluetooth on your phone\r\n   - Press \"Add Device\" in app\r\n   - Follow pairing instructions\r\n   - Wait for confirmation\r\n\r\n#### Network Configuration\r\n1. **Wi-Fi Setup**\r\n   - Open network settings in app\r\n   - Select your Wi-Fi network\r\n   - Enter network password\r\n   - Wait for connection\r\n\r\n2. **Enterprise Network** (Pro/Enterprise)\r\n   - Configure static IP if needed\r\n   - Set up proxy settings\r\n   - Enter network credentials\r\n   - Test connection\r\n\r\n### 3. Basic Operations\r\n\r\n#### Display Navigation\r\n- Swipe left/right: Change screens\r\n- Swipe up/down: Scroll content\r\n- Double-tap: Select item\r\n- Long press: Context menu\r\n\r\n#### Button Configuration\r\n1. **Programming Buttons**\r\n   - Open settings menu\r\n   - Select \"Button Config\"\r\n   - Choose button to program\r\n   - Select desired function\r\n\r\n2. **Quick Actions**\r\n   - Single press: Primary action\r\n   - Double press: Secondary action\r\n   - Long press: Tertiary action\r\n\r\n### 4. Software Setup\r\n\r\n#### Desktop Software\r\n1. **Install the Application**\r\n   - Download from your device manufacturer's website\r\n   - Follow installation wizard\r\n   - Start the application\r\n\r\n2. **Link Your Account**\r\n   - Open desktop application\r\n   - Click \"Sign In\"\r\n   - Use QR code or manual login\r\n   - Verify device connection\r\n\r\n### 5. First Time Usage\r\n\r\n#### Basic Operations\r\n1. **Status Check**\r\n   - Solid Green: Normal operation\r\n   - Blinking Green: Processing/Updating\r\n   - Solid Blue: Bluetooth connected\r\n   - Blinking Blue: Bluetooth pairing mode\r\n   - Solid Red: Error state\r\n   - Blinking Red: Critical error\r\n   - No Light: Power issue\r\n\r\n2. **Initial Calibration**\r\n   - Place on flat surface\r\n   - Enter calibration mode\r\n   - Follow on-screen guide\r\n   - Verify accuracy\r\n\r\n#### Data Configuration\r\n1. **Set Preferences**\r\n   - Time zone\r\n   - Display format\r\n   - Notification settings\r\n   - Power management\r\n\r\n2. **Data Backup**\r\n   - Enable cloud backup\r\n   - Select backup frequency\r\n   - Choose data categories\r\n   - Verify backup status\r\n\r\n## Best Practices\r\n\r\n### Security Setup\r\n1. **Enable Security Features** (Available features depend on tier)\r\n   - Basic Tier:\r\n     - Set up device PIN\r\n     - Configure biometric auth (fingerprint/face)\r\n     - Enable device lock\r\n   - Pro Tier adds:\r\n     - Two-factor authentication\r\n     - Remote lock/wipe capability\r\n   - Enterprise Tier adds:\r\n     - Custom security policies\r\n     - Advanced protection features\r\n\r\n2. **Network Security** (Features vary by tier)\r\n   - Basic Tier:\r\n     - Use secure Wi-Fi\r\n     - Keep firmware updated\r\n   - Pro Tier adds:\r\n     - VPN support\r\n     - Advanced security\r\n   - Enterprise Tier adds:\r\n     - Custom security options\r\n\r\n### Data Management\r\n1. **Storage Setup**\r\n   - Local Storage (varies by tier):\r\n     - Basic: 32GB\r\n     - Pro: 128GB\r\n     - Enterprise: 256GB\r\n   - Cloud Storage:\r\n     - Basic: 10GB\r\n     - Pro: 100GB\r\n     - Enterprise: Custom limits\r\n\r\n2. **Backup Setup** (Features vary by tier)\r\n   - Basic Tier:\r\n     - Daily automated backups\r\n     - 30-day retention\r\n   - Pro Tier:\r\n     - Hourly automated backups\r\n     - 1-year retention\r\n   - Enterprise Tier:\r\n     - Real-time synchronization\r\n     - Custom retention policies\r\n\r\n## Next Steps\r\n\r\n### Additional Features\r\n- Custom automation\r\n- Data analytics\r\n- Device customization\r\n- Advanced settings\r\n\r\n### Learning Resources\r\n- Product documentation\r\n- Video tutorials\r\n- User guides\r\n- Online knowledge base",
