    "content": "# Widget Pricing Guide\r\n\r\n## Standard Pricing Tiers\r\n\r\n### Basic Widget\r\n- **Price**: $99/unit\r\n- **Features**:\r\n  - Standard functionality\r\n  - 1-year warranty\r\n  - Basic support\r\n\r\n### Pro Widget\r\n- **Price**: $199/unit\r\n- **Features**:\r\n  - Advanced functionality\r\n  - 2-year warranty\r\n  - Priority support\r\n  - Custom branding\r\n\r\n### Enterprise Widget\r\n- **Price**: Contact sales\r\n- **Features**:\r\n  - Full feature set\r\n  - 3-year warranty\r\n  - 24/7 dedicated support\r\n  - Integration services\r\n  - Custom development\r\n\r\n## Delivery Options & Timeframes\r\n\r\n### Standard Shipping\r\n- 5-7 business days\r\n- $10 per unit\r\n- Free shipping for orders over $500\r\n\r\n### Express Shipping\r\n- 2-3 business days\r\n- $25 per unit\r\n- Available for urgent orders\r\n\r\n### International Shipping\r\n- 7-14 business days\r\n- Rates vary by location\r\n- Custom clearance assistance available\r\n\r\n## Bulk Order Discounts\r\n\r\n### Volume Discounts\r\n- 10-49 units: 10% off\r\n- 50-99 units: 15% off\r\n- 100+ units: 20% off\r\n\r\n### Annual Contract Discounts\r\n- 1-year contract: Additional 5% off\r\n- 2-year contract: Additional 10% off\r\n- 3-year contract: Additional 15% off\r\n\r\n## Payment Terms\r\n- Net 30 available for qualified businesses\r\n- Multiple payment methods accepted\r\n- Volume pricing requires signed agreement",
