    "content": "# Widget Technical Specifications\r\n\r\n## Physical Specifications\r\n\r\n### Basic Widget\r\n- **Dimensions**: 120mm × 80mm × 40mm\r\n- **Weight**: 250g\r\n- **Material**: Aircraft-grade aluminum\r\n- **Color Options**: Silver, Black, Space Gray\r\n- **Display**: 2.4\" LCD (240 × 320 pixels)\r\n- **Input Methods**: \r\n  - 4 programmable buttons\r\n  - Touch-sensitive scroll wheel\r\n  - USB-C port\r\n\r\n### Pro Widget\r\n- **Dimensions**: 140mm × 90mm × 45mm\r\n- **Weight**: 320g\r\n- **Material**: Titanium alloy\r\n- **Color Options**: All Basic colors + Gold, Rose Gold\r\n- **Display**: 3.5\" OLED (480 × 640 pixels)\r\n- **Input Methods**:\r\n  - 6 programmable buttons\r\n  - Multi-touch trackpad\r\n  - USB-C port\r\n  - Bluetooth 5.0\r\n\r\n### Enterprise Widget\r\n- **Dimensions**: 160mm × 100mm × 50mm\r\n- **Weight**: 400g\r\n- **Material**: Carbon fiber composite\r\n- **Color Options**: Custom branding available\r\n- **Display**: 4.5\" AMOLED (720 × 1280 pixels)\r\n- **Input Methods**:\r\n  - 8 programmable buttons\r\n  - Multi-touch display\r\n  - USB-C port\r\n  - Bluetooth 5.0\r\n  - Wi-Fi 6\r\n\r\n## Technical Requirements\r\n\r\n### Power Specifications\r\n- **Input Voltage**: 5V DC (USB-C)\r\n- **Power Consumption**:\r\n  - Basic: 2.5W typical, 5W max\r\n  - Pro: 4W typical, 7.5W max\r\n  - Enterprise: 6W typical, 12W max\r\n- **Battery**: \r\n  - Basic: 2000mAh Li-ion\r\n  - Pro: 3500mAh Li-ion\r\n  - Enterprise: 5000mAh Li-ion\r\n- **Battery Life**:\r\n  - Basic: 8 hours\r\n  - Pro: 12 hours\r\n  - Enterprise: 16 hours\r\n\r\n### Environmental Requirements\r\n- **Operating Temperature**: 0°C to 40°C\r\n- **Storage Temperature**: -20°C to 60°C\r\n- **Humidity**: 10% to 80% non-condensing\r\n- **IP Rating**: \r\n  - Basic: IP54\r\n  - Pro: IP65\r\n  - Enterprise: IP67\r\n\r\n### Connectivity\r\n\r\n#### Network Requirements\r\n- **Wi-Fi**: \r\n  - Basic: 2.4GHz only\r\n  - Pro: 2.4GHz + 5GHz\r\n  - Enterprise: 2.4GHz + 5GHz + 6GHz\r\n- **Bluetooth**:\r\n  - Basic: Not available\r\n  - Pro: Bluetooth 5.0\r\n  - Enterprise: Bluetooth 5.0 LE\r\n- **Ethernet**: \r\n  - Basic: Not available\r\n  - Pro: 100Mbps\r\n  - Enterprise: 1Gbps\r\n\r\n#### Software Requirements\r\n- **Supported OS**:\r\n  - Windows 10/11\r\n  - macOS 11.0+\r\n  - Linux (Ubuntu 20.04+)\r\n- **Mobile Support**:\r\n  - iOS 14.0+\r\n  - Android 11.0+\r\n\r\n### Security Features\r\n- **Authentication**:\r\n  - Basic: PIN, Biometric (fingerprint/face)\r\n  - Pro: All Basic + 2FA\r\n  - Enterprise: All Basic + Advanced authentication options\r\n- **Device Protection**:\r\n  - Basic: Device Lock\r\n  - Pro: Device Lock/Wipe\r\n  - Enterprise: Advanced security policies\r\n\r\n### Storage & Backup\r\n- **Local Storage**:\r\n  - Basic: 32GB\r\n  - Pro: 128GB\r\n  - Enterprise: 256GB\r\n- **Cloud Storage**:\r\n  - Basic: 10GB\r\n  - Pro: 100GB\r\n  - Enterprise: Configurable storage\r\n- **Backup Frequency**:\r\n  - Basic: Daily automated backups\r\n  - Pro: Hourly automated backups\r\n  - Enterprise: Real-time synchronization\r\n- **Data Retention**:\r\n  - Basic: 30 days\r\n  - Pro: 1 year\r\n  - Enterprise: Configurable retention\r\n\r\n### Maintenance Schedule\r\n- **Calibration Frequency**:\r\n  - Basic: Every 3 months\r\n  - Pro: Every 2 months\r\n  - Enterprise: Monthly or custom schedule\r\n- **System Diagnostics**:\r\n  - Basic: Monthly\r\n  - Pro: Weekly\r\n  - Enterprise: Daily or custom schedule\r\n- **Firmware Updates**:\r\n  - Basic: Quarterly\r\n  - Pro: Monthly\r\n  - Enterprise: As needed\r\n- **Health Checks**:\r\n  - Basic: Automated monthly\r\n  - Pro: Automated weekly\r\n  - Enterprise: Real-time monitoring",
